java.lang.Object

      com.twiddles.ganesha.gui.RDFFileFilter
class RDFFileFilter
extends javax.swing.filechooser.FileFilter

RDF/XML file filter for the file choosing dialogs. Filters out any non-rdf files based on their file extensions.
